 Emma Dickson , of Edinburgh , thought she would be planning her wedding to her fiance Dougie , 26 , but ended up talking to him about her funeral .
The 31-year-old had two blood clots in her lungs , which caused her left lung to collapse - just a month before she was married .
Doctors told she had developed the clot as a result of taking the contraceptive pill .
She was taken to hospital with a collapsed lung , caused a pulmonary embolism .